    Get team

    get_team.Rd

    Get team info

    Usage

    get_team(team_id)

    Arguments

    team_id

    Team ID

    Value

    a data.frame

    Examples

    # \donttest{
sentinels <- get_team(388)
str(sentinels, max.level = 1)
